Based on my thorough read of the bim-ai repository, here are the answers to your specific questions:

### A. ProjectSettingsElem Type - Complete Fields

**Location:** `/Users/jhoetter/repos/bim-ai/packages/core/src/index.ts` lines 1055-1076

```typescript
