  environment: 'jsdom',
  coverage: { provider: 'v8', ... },
},
```

Run with: `npm run test` (turbo task) or `vitest run src` in web package.

**Test files located:** `/Users/jhoetter/repos/bim-ai/packages/web/src/viewport/*.test.ts` (e.g., `meshBuilders.ts` has no separate test file, but individual builders have paired `.test.ts` files like `meshBuilders.mass.test.ts`).

### I. Project Settings Panel in Web UI

**Location:** `/Users/jhoetter/repos/bim-ai/packages/web/src/workspace/inspector/InspectorContent.tsx` lines 3212-3272

The panel is `InspectorProjectSettingsEditor`, a React component that renders:
- Checkpoint Retention (number input)
- Volume Computed At (dropdown: finish_faces / core_faces)
- Room Area Computation (dropdown: wall_finish / wall_centerline / wall_core_layer / wall_core_center)

It's invoked from `/Users/jhoetter/repos/bim-ai/packages/web/src/workspace/WorkspaceRightRail.tsx` when element kind is `'project_settings'`.

